qDes: click on all the dots and the climb the monkey up the tree to get the most points

When the chart tells you to click on the second row, you click on the second row. It lets you decide which path you want to take and how many risks you're willing to take. It's a guessing game when you follow the flow chart, but clicking on all of the nodes lets you know which way is a guaranteed profit.

I mean its just a study, but I found myself in that same situation half the time if not the whole time. So being a lose lose situation.  Just my +2 cents.
